a structure like this. The forces on Elysium
would be similar to the ISS, other than the

00:04:29.260 --> 00:04:33.650
additional stress created by centripetal and
centrifugal force. It’s interesting to note

00:04:33.650 --> 00:04:37.630
that the designers of Elysium took note of
this. The stress in a spinning structure like

00:04:37.630 --> 00:04:41.780
this would decrease as you move away from
the rotational center. This means it would

00:04:41.780 --> 00:04:46.010
need a stronger structure the closer you get
to the center. This clearly influenced their

00:04:46.010 --> 00:04:50.570
design with these tapering spokes. But we
